text: __FORCETOC__ Tidofeld has been an autonomous part of the East Frisian borough of Norden since 1996 and has about 1,000 residents (as at 12/2016)), spread over an area of just 0.47 km². Its built-up area is completely connected with the town itself. Until 1952, Tidofeld was part of the municipality of Lütetsburg. == References == Category:Aurich (district)
title: Tidofeld
